  "page": "A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 34",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background-color:rgb(230, 230, 230)\">Bran III</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons\">A Dance with Dragons</a></i> chapter</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_dance_with_dragons\" title=\"A dance with dragons\"><img alt=\"ADanceWithDragons.jpg\" src=\"/images/7/79/ADanceWithDragons.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"337\" class=\"thumbborder\" /></a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">POV</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Cave_of_the_three-eyed_crow\" title=\"Cave of the three-eyed crow\">Cave of the three-eyed crow</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Page</th><td>\n448 <small>UK HC</small> <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters_Table_of_contents\" title=\"Chapters Table of contents\">Other versions</a>)</small></td></tr><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;background-color:rgb(230, 230, 230)\">Chapter chronology <small>(<a href=\"/index.php/Chapters\" title=\"Chapters\">All</a>)</small></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_13\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 13\">Bran II</a><br />↑</td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%;\"><tbody><tr>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_33\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 33\">Tyrion VIII</a></td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">&#160;←</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle; padding-right:0.1em; padding-left:0.1em;\">Bran III</td>\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle;\">→&#160;</td>\n<td style=\"width:33%; text-align:center; vertical-align:middle;\"><a href=\"/index.php/A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_35\" title=\"A Dance with Dragons-Chapter 35\">Jon VII</a></td>\n</tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Synopsis\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Synopsis</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Notes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Notes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#External_links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External links</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Synopsis\">Synopsis</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_34&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Synopsis\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"thumb tleft\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:252px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Marc_Fishman_thevision.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/Marc_Fishman_thevision.jpg/250px-Marc_Fishman_thevision.jpg\" width=\"250\" height=\"284\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/c/c9/Marc_Fishman_thevision.jpg/375px-Marc_Fishman_thevision.jpg 1.5x, /images/c/c9/Marc_Fishman_thevision.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Marc_Fishman_thevision.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A white haired woman with a bronze sickle - by Marc Fishman ©</div></div></div>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Hodor\" title=\"Hodor\">Hodor</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera</a> are still dwelling in the <a href=\"/index.php/Cave_of_the_three-eyed_crow\" title=\"Cave of the three-eyed crow\">cave</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Children_of_the_Forest\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Children of the Forest\">children of the Forest</a> and exploring its chambers. Bran uses his ability as a <a href=\"/index.php/Skinchanger\" title=\"Skinchanger\">warg and skinchanger</a> to enter <a href=\"/index.php/Summer\" title=\"Summer\">Summer</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Hodor\" title=\"Hodor\">Hodor</a>. They begin to name some of the \"children\" as their own names are unpronounceable by the human tongue. Bran names one of the females <a href=\"/index.php/Leaf\" title=\"Leaf\">Leaf</a>, as she is always adorned with leaves. She is one of the few children who can speak the <a href=\"/index.php/Common_Tongue\" title=\"Common Tongue\">Common Tongue</a>. Others are called <a href=\"/index.php/Ash\" title=\"Ash\">Ash</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Scales\" title=\"Scales\">Scales</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Black_Knife\" title=\"Black Knife\">Black Knife</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Snowylocks\" title=\"Snowylocks\">Snowylocks</a>, and <a href=\"/index.php/Coals\" title=\"Coals\">Coals</a>.\n</p><p><a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen</a> is growing extremely sad and solemn, and still has fits of shaking. His sister <a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera</a> does her best to keep up the spirits of both her brother and Bran.\n</p><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Three-eyed_crow\" title=\"Three-eyed crow\">three-eyed crow</a> teaches <a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran</a> how to enter into ravens. He learns that all of the ravens around the three-eyed crow have children who have passed away and remain in the skins of these animals. He also learns to use <a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood\" title=\"Weirwood\">weirwoods</a> to look into the past. The three-eyed crow tells Bran that he was once a lord called Brynden. \n</p><p>The children feed Bran a bowl of <a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood_paste\" title=\"Weirwood paste\">weirwood paste</a> to awaken his green seeing gifts. Bran sees his father, <a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard</a>, through <a href=\"/index.php/Winterfell\" title=\"Winterfell\">Winterfell</a>'s heart tree, and learns that he can view the past, present and future through the weirwoods. The last greenseer tells Bran that he is haunted by his own ghosts, a brother that he loved, a brother that he hated, and a woman that he desired,<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;N 1&#93;</a></sup> but knows from experience that you cannot change the past. When he gets tired, he sends Bran away. Hodor carries Bran to his bed. \n</p><p>In his sleep, Bran sees the following visions through Winterfell's heart tree:\n</p>\n<ul><li>His young <a href=\"/index.php/Ned_Stark\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Ned Stark\">father</a> praying with a bowed head \"…let them grow up close as brothers, with only love between them, and let my <a href=\"/index.php/Catelyn_Stark\" title=\"Catelyn Stark\">lady wife</a> find it in her heart to forgive.\";<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;N 2&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>A girl and a younger boy play fighting with branches;<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;N 3&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>A pregnant woman coming out of the black pool praying for a son to avenge her;</li>\n<li>A slender girl on her toes kissing a <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> as tall as Hodor;<sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;N 4&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li>A pale, dark-eyed youth cutting three branches from the weirwood and shaping them into arrows;</li>\n<li>Other lords of Winterfell: tall, hard, stern men in fur and chain mail;</li>\n<li>A bearded man forcing a captive down on his knees, and a white-haired woman killing the captive with a bronze sickle.</li></ul>\n<h2><span id=\"Character_List_appearing/mentioned\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Character_List_appearing.2Fmentioned\">Character List appearing/mentioned</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_34&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Character List appearing/mentioned\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"column-count:3; column-width:300px;\"> \n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Bran_Stark\" title=\"Bran Stark\">Bran Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jojen_Reed\" title=\"Jojen Reed\">Jojen Reed</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Meera_Reed\" title=\"Meera Reed\">Meera Reed</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Leaf\" title=\"Leaf\">Leaf</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Summer\" title=\"Summer\">Summer</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Hodor\" title=\"Hodor\">Hodor</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Rivers\" title=\"Brynden Rivers\">Brynden Rivers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Snowylocks\" title=\"Snowylocks\">Snowylocks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Eddard_Stark\" title=\"Eddard Stark\">Eddard Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Ash\" title=\"Ash\">Ash</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Scales\" title=\"Scales\">Scales</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Black_Knife\" title=\"Black Knife\">Black Knife</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Coals\" title=\"Coals\">Coals</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Stark\" title=\"Jon Stark\">Jon Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Sansa_Stark\" title=\"Sansa Stark\">Sansa Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Rickon_Stark\" title=\"Rickon Stark\">Rickon Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maester_Luwin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maester Luwin\">Maester Luwin</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II Targaryen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Aegor_Rivers\" title=\"Aegor Rivers\">Aegor Rivers</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Shiera_Seastar\" title=\"Shiera Seastar\">Shiera Seastar</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Notes\">Notes</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=A_Dance_with_Dragons-Chapter_34&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Notes\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">If the Three-Eyed Crow is indeed <a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Rivers\" title=\"Brynden Rivers\">Brynden Rivers</a>, as implied, then the loved brother is probably <a href=\"/index.php/Daeron_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Daeron II Targaryen\">Daeron II</a>, the hated brother is probably <a href=\"/index.php/Aegor_Rivers\" title=\"Aegor Rivers\">Aegor \"Bittersteel\" Rivers</a> or perhaps <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_I_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon I Blackfyre\">Daemon Blackfyre</a>, and the woman must be <a href=\"/index.php/Shiera_Seastar\" title=\"Shiera Seastar\">Shiera Seastar</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Probably shortly after his return from <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>, referring to <a href=\"/index.php/Robb_Stark\" title=\"Robb Stark\">Robb Stark</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Possibly Bran's uncle <a href=\"/index.php/Benjen_Stark\" title=\"Benjen Stark\">Benjen Stark</a> and late aunt <a href=\"/index.php/Lyanna_Stark\" title=\"Lyanna Stark\">Lyanna Stark</a>; Bran finds the girl to be alike to his sister <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">Arya</a>, who is said to remind people of a young Lyanna as per <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_22\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 22\">Chapter 22</a>.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">It is believed to be <a href=\"/index.php/Dunk\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Dunk\">Dunk</a> kissing a young woman, possibly a young <a href=\"/index.php/Old_Nan\" title=\"Old Nan\">Old Nan</a>, at Winterfell, foreshadowing the next <a href=\"/index.php/Dunk_and_Egg\" title=\"Dunk and Egg\">Dunk and Egg</a> story, <i><a href=\"/index.php/The_She-Wolves_of_Winterfell\" title=\"The She-Wolves of Winterfell\">The She-Wolves of Winterfell</a></i>.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_links\">External links</span><span class=\"mw-editsec